title: The Decline of Influence and Avoiding Entitlement | Gary Vay
description:
Gary Vaynerchuk is an entrepreneur and best-selling author of "Jab, Jab, Jab Right-Hook," specializing in social media and marketing. Here he talks to Will Cain for "The Cain Conversation" about influence, expectation and entitlement.
